European Nautical Platform; the platform for sharing nautical topics, best practices, ways of working, positions and opinions in the field of nautical operations in port water and their approaches.&#xd;
The Platform is a cooperation between the European organizations of Captains, Pilots, Tug operators, boatmen and Harbour Masters. These nautical experts combine forces to address nautical safety from pilot station to berth.&#xd;
